      "amount": "a pinch"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and ginger, sauté for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add finely chopped onions to the pan and cook until translucent.",
    "Gradually add semolina flour, stirring constantly to avoid lumps.",
    "Stir in salt and white pepper to taste. Cook for another minute.",
    "Serve hot as a snack or breakfast with a side of fresh fruits or yogurt."
